emuInput.TitMainTitle: Groom Jesse T. Henderson Jr. and bride Amanda Bussey Henderson seated in automobile
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 15, 1951, pg. 10 reads: " Mrs. Jesse T. Henderson - Harris Photo." Portion of accompanying article reads: "Mary Amanda Bussey, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. James Bussey of Singer Place, was married on Sept. 1 at Trinity AME Church to Jesse T. Hendersosn [Henderson] Jr., son of Mr. and Mrs. Jesse T. Henderson, Amsterdam, N.Y."
